snippet.title: Best VGM 2161 - Sonic CD - Tidal Tempest (US)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1346 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CYswIEEMIWw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega CD
Sonic the Hedgehog CD (1993)
Tidal Tempest (US)
Spencer Nilsen
